Movie/Show Synopsis: In Denmark, during the 6th century, Danish king Hrothgar and his warriors kill a troll whose son, Grendel, vows revenge.
Movie/Show Sales Pitch: An epic, blood-soaked, mystical tale of redemption and vengance, Beowulf and Grendel stars Gerard Butler (300, Den of Thieves), Ingvar E Sigurðsson (Godland, The Northman), and Stellan Skarsgård (Dune). Visually stunning and tough-as-nails.
Cast: Gerard Butler, Stellan Skarsgård, Ingvar Sigurdsson, Gunnar Eyjólfsson, Philip Whitchurch, Ronan Vibert, Rory McCann, Sarah Polley
Producer(s): Sturla Gunnarsson, Gary Hamilton, Eric Jordan, Anna María Karlsdóttir, Fridrik Thor Fridriksson
Tag(s): King, beowulf, gerard butler, revenge, warrior
